  <!-- Section 6: CalHFA vs other programs -->
  <h2 id="calhfa-vs-others">CalHFA vs. Other Down Payment Assistance Programs</h2>
  <p>
    CalHFA is not the only source of down payment assistance in San Diego. Here is how it compares to other options:
  </p>
  <ComparisonTable
    headers={["Program", "Max Assistance", "Repayment", "Geographic Scope", "Key Advantage"]}
